Kisauni MP Rashid Bedzimba has dismissed claims his rival Ali Mbogo will be given ODM direct nomination for the area MP seat.Earlier this month, Mbogo said ODM leader Raila Odinga had promised him a direct nomination after he accompanied him to Germany on a business trip.Bedzimba on Saturday said Mbogo s remarks proves "he is coward" and not ready to face him or any other person at the party primaries.